Package: BiocOffPiste
Title: Help users of Bioconductor who want to combine versions of 
	R and Bioconductor not supported by BiocManager
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Vince",
           family = "Carey",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stvjc@channing.harvard.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4046-0063"))
Description: This package helps arrange repository selection so that R-devel
	and Bioconductor can be used together during the period in which
	BiocManager::install will only work on R-patched.  The package
	defines installOffPiste, which is intended only for expeRts.
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0), tools, utils, BiocManager
Suggests: knitr, BiocStyle, testthat, rmarkdown
License: Artistic-2.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: Infrastructure
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/vjcitn/BiocOffPiste
BugReports: https://github.com/vjcitn/BiocOffPiste/issues
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
